onsistent availability and quality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aBread industryxSubsidieszEgypt. 0aBreadxGovernment policyzEgypt. 0aBreadxSocial aspectszEgypt. 0aFood securityzEgypt. 0aFood supplyzEgypt. 0aWheat tradexSocial aspectszEgypt. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh1 aTaher, Mariam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478023111?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478023111423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478023111/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles